Package: hurricanesotr
Title: Plots Single Observation Time Dataset for single Storm
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hugo", "Nomanyon", , "hugostar84@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package provides stat, geom and other functions to help create 
   and plot a single observation time dataset of a single storm. It relies on 
   storms data in the Extended Best Tract dataset as database. An url will be 
   provided to download this dataset.
